title: How A Chicago Salon Owner Is Changing The Hair Care Industry, One Cut At A Time | Insider Business
description:
Sponsored content by American Express 

At Logan Parlor in Chicago, “men’s” and “women’s” cuts don’t exist. Instead, pricing is based on factors like timing, length, and stylist level — not gender. Jamie DiGrazia, the visionary owner, is at the forefront of working to reshape the haircare industry into a more inclusive space for everyone.
